  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Rex is in the perfect location for exploring Naples. It's close to the waterfront where there's lots of local restaurants where you can try the city's famous pizza. You can walk to most of the sights from here and there's good public transport links close by too.</p>]]></listingDescription>
